# Development Philosophy

composition gang of four

 

simple

embrace fallibility

frameworks should do their best to stay out of your way, providing minimal limits on creativity.
they should handle the things that are onerous, that are easy to screw up, the things that can have hidden consequences.


resource contention -- not ioc, command clear military hierarchy, ambiguous leadership kind of bites 
file management 
house cleaning and the state of my listeners
race conditions
error handling
encapsulation and coupling -- pipes and valves

rogue pragmatism
dependency declaration


 
